---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Sweet Temptations - Boutique Cakery | Whanganui, New Zealand
description: Sweet Temptations is a boutique cakery in Whanganui, New Zealand. We create personalised cakes, cupcakes, cookies and much more for weddings, birthdays, and all special occasions.
---

<main class="homepage">
  {# Hero Section #}
  <section class="hero relative py-16 md:py-24 bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('/assets/images/home-hero.jpeg');">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-30"></div>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        {# Hero Content #}
        <div class="hero__content">
          <h2 class="font-accent text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-white leading-tight mb-6 drop-shadow-lg">
            Life is better with sprinkles on top!
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white mb-8 drop-shadow-md">
            We're a boutique cakery who create personalised cakes, cupcakes, 
            cookies and much more!
          </p>
          <a href="/gallery/" class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-[#fa7598] text-white rounded-md font-medium hover:bg-[#e66387] transition-colors text-lg shadow-lg">
            See some of our creations
          </a>
        </div>

        {# Hero Image Placeholder - Hidden with background image #}
        <div class="hero__image hidden md:block">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# Introduction Section #}
  <section class="intro py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        {# Logo/Image #}
        <div class="intro__image flex justify-center">
          <div class="w-64 h-64 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[#62cbc9] to-[#fa7598] p-8 flex items-center justify-center border-8 border-[#fa7598]">
            <div class="w-full h-full rounded-full bg-[#62cbc9] flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-32 h-32 text-white" fill="currentColor">
                <path d="M12 2L11 6L10 10L11 14L12 18L13 14L14 10L13 6L12 2ZM8 4L7 8L8 12L9 8L8 4ZM16 4L15 8L16 12L17 8L16 4ZM4 6L3 10L4 14L5 10L4 6ZM20 6L19 10L20 14L21 10L20 6ZM12 20L10 21L12 22L14 21L12 20Z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {# Content #}
        <div class="intro__content">
          <h2 class="font-accent text-3xl md:text-4xl text-[#fa7598] mb-6">
            Hi there!
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            I'm Emma Tipper, the founder of Sweet Temptations. I run a boutique cakery 
            working with you to create sweet treats for all occasions including weddings, 
            baby showers, birthdays and other events.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We create custom cakes, cupcakes, cookies and much more! I have loved creating 
            in the kitchen for as long as I can remember. The joy and smile a homemade treat 
            can bring someone is such a special feeling.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            In my spare time I love baking, gardening, flowers, exercising and people - a 
            great combo to help me bring your ideas to life. I look forward to working with 
            you! Talk soon, Emma xx
          </p>
          <a href="/contact-us/" class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-[#fa7598] text-white rounded-md font-medium hover:bg-[#fa7598] transition-colors">
            Talk to us today
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# About Section #}
  <section class="about py-16 bg-[#F8F8F8]">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        Sweet Temptations is a boutique baker serving the Whanganui region. 
        We make personalised cakes, cupcakes, cookies and much more!{" "}
        <a href="/contact-us/" class="text-[#62cbc9] hover:text-[#62cbc9] underline transition-colors">
          Talk to us today
        </a>{" "}
        about your ideas.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# What We Do Section #}
  <section class="services py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="font-accent text-3xl md:text-4xl text-[#62cbc9] text-center mb-12">
        what we do
      </h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        {% set services = ["Weddings", "Birthdays", "Corporate Events", "Celebrations", "Catering", "Thankyous"] %}
        {% for service in services %}
        <div class="service-item text-center">
          <h3 class="font-accent text-xl md:text-2xl text-[#62cbc9]">
            {{ service }}
          </h3>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# CTA Section #}
  <section class="cta py-16 bg-[#FFB6D1] text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-accent text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-6">
        Ready to create something special?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg mb-8">
        Let's bring your vision to life with a custom creation made just for you.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/gallery/" class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-white text-[#fa7598] rounded-md font-medium hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
          View Gallery
        </a>
        <a href="/contact-us/" class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-white text-[#fa7598] rounded-md font-medium hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
          Contact Us
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
